window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Welcome to the first Haunted Guest House mystery - the getaway every reader can afford. </p> <p>Newly divorced Alison Kerby wants a second chance for herself and her nine-year-old daughter. She's returned to her hometown on the Jersey Shore to transform a Victorian fixer-upper into a charming-and profitable guest house. One small problem: the house is haunted, and the two ghosts insist Alison must find out who killed them. </p>"; 
